Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:33.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(464.857,119.906)\fad(1900,1900)}Mushishi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone... don't use that fire to warm yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is my punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:25.23,Default,,90,0,0,,{\i1}Should I have done as that man had said?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:29.98,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.22,0:01:29.98,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\be1}The Journey to the Field of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's a mushi-shi in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he talking about Yahagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's with daddy and the others in the plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of weeds we've never \Nseen before have been growing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and are withering the trees on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to split up and cut down\Nthe trees surrounding the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you not to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You've gotten hurt again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've brought a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't touch that weed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... It would be easy to overlook\Nif it was just this one growing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but with this many, it would be hard \Nnot to notice these are mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... a mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that a new species had appeared around here so I thought I'd investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But the investigation has already come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:10.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the name Yahagi sounded familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read some transcripts of your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be such a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your report on that mushi \Nmust be quite impressive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incomplete, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Incomplete? You just said earlier\Nthat it had come to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any need to investigate anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,since we're going to burn the entire mountain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to burn the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Isn't it only that weed that's no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the animals on the mountain going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked everyone to try their best to shoo them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave that weed alone any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the mountain and even your lives will be endangered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our last chance for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be something I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me what's been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We were digging up the soil to \Nclear that plain for farmland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A large black boulder then surfaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're near a volcano, there area lot of volcanic rocks in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We dug it up and left it in a corner\Nof the plain as we usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, I noticed a weed was growing out from a crack in the boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the time, I gave no heed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days later, the rain had cleared
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and we found that the plain \Nwas overrun with those weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed that their roots were connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much we cut and pulled at them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd grow back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I realized it was \Nsomething unnatural, it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Their blossoms released a poison
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and started withering the surrounding plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Their vigor never wanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to exterminate them in many different ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have yet to find anything that works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The weed has spread throughout the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and is even spreading towards our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, the price for burning\Nthe entire mountain is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it's an unknown mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what kind of consequences there will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should try to gather as many people as possible and pull them out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how much time it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just let our crops wither,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,this village won't be able to survive the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's lives are at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then even more so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we should ignore some casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that if you're going to take a gamble, don't risk others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A fair argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But the frightened villagers won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there is no meaning to that reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that you're vexed about not having identified that mushi immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but what good will it do if you become fearful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural to want to protect\Nthe people of your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to use any means for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you that report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it will be useful to you \Nin your future investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave us already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww... they cut the big camphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry tree is gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you plan to sacrifice\Nfor the sake of your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you. Please think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard for us to destroy the forest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a life or death situation for us and our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mushi-shi from elsewhere, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a great mushi-shi in this village as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What would an outsider know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From an outsider's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you look like a frightened tribe of monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose all sight of your surroundings\Nout of fear and blindly attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not monkeys, why don't\N you try to face your fears?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't people begin to use fire in order to do just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying conquer your fear with intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also intelligence that\Nallowed people to approach fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shallow intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I already told you to leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I found that weed at the edge of our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry with the deforestation and set the mountain on fire tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I went a bit too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's well researched, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For that reason alone, she must regret that her only option is to burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good coming from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only you can put a stop to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That mushi was inside a volcanic rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get the feeling that we shouldn't set it on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's set the fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But we sure burned everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... is this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Quickly! Back to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that fire get near your homes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Turn over all of your containers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out and tell your neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, those fireballs will nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as he says! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing looks like fire, \Nbut it's something called {\i1}kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears on rainy and cold days
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and gradually steals body heat\Nfrom those who approach it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,mistaking it to be fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On warm days,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it will lurk in narrow spaces,\Nlike in pots or hollows in trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them probably have nested already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, be careful when you approach fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You may end up freezing to death if you unwittingly stay near it too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly are we supposed to be careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If a fire feels lukewarm, assume it is {\i1}kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the {\i1}kagebi{\i0} is a mushi called the {\i1}Hidane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That mushi is the {\i1}kagebi's{\i0} true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It thrives by absorbing humans' heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just be careful, you won't be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have gotten troublesome, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought that\Nthose weeds were {\i1}Hidane{\i0} larvae?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can deal with {\i1}Hidane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read about them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate for you that it wasn't a new species.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must be happy that you \Nlearned its larva's ecology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take your frustration out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagebi{\i0} are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one in the village who can deal with them, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If things get beyond your control,\Nsend a letter here. I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in return for the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take on too much by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... crap. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll light a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... it won't light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A left-over fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is sure cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The room won't warm at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems the weeds have been exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They probably won't sprout up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's just the kagebi left to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yahagi-chan!{\i0} My child has become so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our old man, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The folks next door are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And many have suffered frostbite in their guts by food cooked by {\i1}kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had warned them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:17:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with a sore gut should recover soon with rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is now being very cautious,\Nso casualties have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the ridding of the {\i1}kagebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By crushing the {\i1}Hidane,{\i0} they soon disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be rid of most of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the mushi gets killed, so does the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as the writings say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've discovered the ecology not in the writings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When one consumes enough heat\Nand lives its full lifespan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,those weeds are born again from its remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want me to help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do that by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to go to somewhere desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When we burned the mountain, I inhaled a {\i1}kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A person's body can also serve as a container, can't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been lurking there, \Nslowly sapping away my body heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My body felt like it was freezing for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I've begun to cough up weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my punishment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Hidane{\i0} have sprouted in my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also began to spit poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told the rest of the village that there's not much time left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of leaving the village to find \Na place to die before my body is taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I wish to leave the village in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a mistake would never\Nhappen again with you in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I would have said\Nthe same thing in your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a battle that you all started,\Nwhich will continue from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a problem to just end it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I've long been thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to catch a {\i1}kagebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that going to make Yahagi better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the {\i1}Hidane{\i0} are well made?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The behavior of spitting poison was likely by chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can make people set them on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaining fire, they mature and use it to lure people in to steal their body heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, man, the only animal\Nthat uses fire, is used by this fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, {\i1}Hidane{\i0} are just imitation fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that the larvae will mature if we set this imitation fire upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to get rid of that weed,\Nwhy not just burn them with {\i1}kagebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Food which has been heated by {\i1}kagebi{\i0}\Nalso likely has the same effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,While burning my gut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I ate that too, \Nand my gut hurt as if it were on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It burned the weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,More, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body won't hold up if you rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get better gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1480)}Slowly and surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}coughing up weeds and burning her gut...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hear that she continues to live protecting the village
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from the unnatural beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, we don't see many {\i1}kagebi{\i0} anymore, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because it's gotten warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know where they lurk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying towards the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be searching for the coldest place it can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And holding its breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It patiently waits for winter to come.
